These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, cola
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, rock, house
1. the fan of rock is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the fan of house and the person drinking iced-tea##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | cola | milk |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | indie    | house   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, skydiving, cooking
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, scientist, chef
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the chef is between the manager and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | cooking        | skydiving |
| Job     | scientist | chef | manager         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, lemonade
3 different pets are kept: bird, goat, rat
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking coffee is between the owner of the goat and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | fanta | coffee     | lemonade |
| Pet        | goat  | rat | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, house, ambient
3 different pets are kept: goat, chinchilla, frog
1. the fan of hip-hop is the owner of the goat##1
2. the fan of ambient is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the goat##2
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | house  | ambient     | hip-hop |
| Pet           | chinchilla | frog | goat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, dancing, rock-climbing
3 different pets are kept: pony, bird, cat
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | dancing | rock-climbing     | traveling |
| Pet     | cat    | pony | bird    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, polish, australian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, golf, cycling
1. the person who's sport is badminton is between the australian and the mexican##2
2. the mexican is the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the polish is on the right of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | mexican  | polish   | australian        |
| Sport         | golf | badminton | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, peach, raspberry
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, turkish, japanese
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
2. the pakistani is between the person eating raspberry and the turkish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | peach  | artichoke  | raspberry |
| Nationality   | turkish | pakistani | japanese     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, disaster
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani, turkish
1. the person watching mystery movies is the turkish##1
2. the pakistani is between the person watching mystery movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | fantasy  | mystery  |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, golf, handball
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, bike, airplane
1. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the person who's sport is handball and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | handball | baseball | golf  |
| Transport   | airplane    | subway        | bike |

