.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, water, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: pepper, carrot, radish
1. the person eating radish is between the person drinking water and the person eating pepper##2
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | water | juice      | soy-milk      |
| Food       | carrot  | radish | pepper |

