.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: french, german, british
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, lacrosse, soccer
1. the person who's sport is rugby is between the german and the british##2
2. the german is on the far left##1
3. the german is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | german | french   | british   |
| Sport         | soccer  | rugby | lacrosse |

