.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, juice
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, metal, country
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the fan of metal##2
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | juice | lemonade   | milk |
| Music-Genre   | country  | d&b | metal   |

 